R`ndomText is a tool designers and developers can use to quickly grab dummy text in either Lorem Ipsum or Gibberish format.



Grab HTML or just plain text - even save generated text as files:
Don't
 waste time copying tdxt and then more time marking it up in HTML manually, just hit View HTML Code and then Copy to Clipboard!

Use the address bar to create a query:
Don't waste more time fiddling with form options! RandomText `llows you to get at your text quicker by using the URL to construct a query...
randomtext*
randomtext.me / lorem / ul--81185954333 / 18446744073709551616-32782 /
randomtext.me / gibberish / p-0 / 32767-170141183460469231731687303715884105682 /
randomtext.me / lorem / h2147483647 / 7-10 /
